<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>MBO649 Capstone — Start Tomorrow</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,400;1,9..144,500&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #1c1814;
    --ink-soft: #4a443d;
    --paper: #f6f1e4;
    --paper-deep: #ede5d1;
    --paper-edge: #d8cfb8;
    --saffron: #b54a2c;
    --saffron-deep: #8a3520;
    --sage: #6b7a52;
    --sage-deep: #4a5638;
    --plum: #6b2737;
    --muted: #8a8275;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-size: 15px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .wrap {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 36px 32px 80px;
  }

  /* ---------- MASTHEAD ---------- */
  .masthead {
    border-top: 3px solid var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding: 12px 0 10px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .masthead .left { font-weight: 600; }
  .masthead .right { color: var(--muted); }

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero {
    padding: 72px 0 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 110px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
  }
  .lede {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.45;
    max-width: 720px;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  /* ---------- THE PLAN ----------*/
  .plan {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .section-head {
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 60px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--saffron-deep); font-weight: 400; }
  .section-sub {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 660px;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  /* ---------- TRACKS GRID ---------- */
  .tracks-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .track-card {
    padding: 32px 28px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  .track-card:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .track-card.t0 { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }
  .track-card.t0 .tag { color: var(--saffron); border-color: var(--saffron); }
  .track-card.t0 h3 { color: var(--paper); }
  .track-card.t0 .who { color: rgba(246, 241, 228, 0.7); }
  .track-card.t0 .whatfor { color: rgba(246, 241, 228, 0.85); }
  .track-card.t0 .deadlines { border-top-color: rgba(246, 241, 228, 0.25); }
  .track-card.t0 .deadlines li { border-top-color: rgba(246, 241, 228, 0.18); color: var(--paper); }
  .track-card.t0 .deadlines small { color: rgba(246, 241, 228, 0.6); }
  .track-card.t0 .marks-line { color: var(--saffron); border-top-color: rgba(246, 241, 228, 0.25); }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 5px 9px;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .track-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .track-card .who {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .track-card .whatfor {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .track-card .deadlines {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(28,24,20,0.25);
  }
  .track-card .deadlines li {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(28,24,20,0.18);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .track-card .deadlines li:first-child { border-top: none; }
  .track-card .deadlines small {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .marks-line {
    margin-top: 14px;
    padding-top: 12px;
    border-top: 1px dashed rgba(28,24,20,0.25);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ---------- TOMORROW BLOCK ---------- */
  .tomorrow {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .day-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .day-row {
    display: contents;
  }
  .day-row .when {
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper-deep);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .day-row .when .label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .day-row .when .when-name {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 26px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .day-row .when .when-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
  }
  .day-row .when .dates {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .day-row .what {
    padding: 28px 30px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .day-row .what .group {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .day-row .what .group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .day-row .what .group-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .day-row .what ul {
    list-style: none;
  }
  .day-row .what li {
    padding: 6px 0 6px 22px;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .day-row .what li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 6px;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ---------- CALENDAR ---------- */
  .calendars {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .legend-mini {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .legend-mini .item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .legend-mini .sw {
    width: 16px;
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .legend-mini .sw.deadline { background: var(--saffron); }
  .legend-mini .sw.target { border: 2px solid var(--sage-deep); background: transparent; }
  .legend-mini .sw.note { background: var(--paper-deep); border: 1px solid var(--ink); }

  .month-block {
    padding: 36px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .month-block:first-of-type { border-top: 1px solid var(--ink); margin-top: 0; }

  .month-head {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    padding-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .month-name {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 48px;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  }
  .month-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    margin-left: 4px;
  }
  .month-meta {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .cal {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .cal .dow {
    padding: 8px 6px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cal .day {
    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
    padding: 8px 8px 4px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: var(--paper);
    min-height: 64px;
  }
  .cal .day.out {
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, var(--paper), var(--paper) 4px, var(--paper-edge) 4px, var(--paper-edge) 5px);
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .cal .day .num {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .cal .day.out .num {
    color: var(--paper-edge);
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  .cal .day .tag-d {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 8.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: auto;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cal .day.deadline { background: var(--saffron); color: #fff; }
  .cal .day.deadline .num { color: #fff; font-weight: 500; }
  .cal .day.deadline .tag-d { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.92); font-weight: 600; }
  .cal .day.target { background: var(--paper); }
  .cal .day.target .num {
    color: var(--sage-deep);
    font-weight: 500;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .cal .day.target .num::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -4px -6px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--sage-deep);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  .cal .day.target .tag-d { color: var(--sage-deep); font-weight: 600; }
  .cal .day.note { background: var(--paper-deep); }
  .cal .day.note .tag-d { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

  .sidebar {
    padding-top: 8px;
  }
  .sidebar .theme {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--saffron);
    padding-left: 16px;
  }
  .sidebar .summary {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    padding-left: 18px;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .sidebar .focus-list {
    list-style: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .sidebar .focus-list li {
    padding: 14px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(28,24,20,0.18);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  .sidebar .focus-list .d-num {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-align: right;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .sidebar .focus-list li.deadline-r .d-num { color: var(--saffron-deep); }
  .sidebar .focus-list li.target-r .d-num { color: var(--sage-deep); }
  .sidebar .focus-list li.note-r .d-num { color: var(--ink); }
  .sidebar .focus-list .d-info {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.45;
  }
  .sidebar .focus-list .d-info small {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 3px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ---------- DON'T FAIL ---------- */
  .dontfail {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .fail-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .fail-list .item {
    padding: 22px 26px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .fail-list .item:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
  .fail-list .item:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }
  .fail-list .item .num {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--saffron-deep);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .fail-list .item h5 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 17px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .fail-list .item p {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
  footer {
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--ink);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10.5px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  /* ---------- RESPONSIVE ---------- */
  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .wrap { padding: 22px 16px 60px; }
    .hero { padding: 44px 0 36px; }
    .lede { font-size: 18px; padding-left: 18px; }
    .tracks-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .track-card { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink); }
    .track-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .day-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .day-row .when { border-right: none; padding: 20px 22px 14px; }
    .day-row .what { padding: 20px 22px; }
    .month-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; padding: 28px 0; }
    .month-name { font-size: 36px; }
    .cal .day { padding: 5px 5px 3px; min-height: 50px; }
    .cal .day .num { font-size: 14px; }
    .cal .day .tag-d { font-size: 7.5px; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
    .cal .day.target .num::after { inset: -3px -4px; }
    .fail-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .fail-list .item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink); }
    .fail-list .item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <div class="masthead">
    <div class="left">MBO649 · Capstone Planner · For the batch</div>
    <div class="right">Starts tomorrow · Ends 26 July 2026</div>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Read this once. Then start.</div>
    <h1>Tomorrow you start. <em>Here's how it goes.</em></h1>
    <div class="lede">
      The capstone is not one thing — it's three layers running at the same time. One of them quietly carries 30 marks and has to start tomorrow or it will not finish in time. This page lays out all three, in the order you actually have to act on them.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- THE THREE LAYERS -->
  <div class="plan">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-num">§ 01 — The shape of it</div>
      <h2>Three layers. <em>Choose one of two.</em></h2>
      <div class="section-sub">Track 0 is mandatory and runs the whole semester for everyone. On top of that, you pick exactly one of Track 1 or Track 2. That's the entire structure.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="tracks-3">

      <!-- TRACK 0 -->
      <div class="track-card t0">
        <span class="tag">Track 0 · Everyone</span>
        <h3>The Coursera layer.</h3>
        <p class="who">Officially called "Step 0." Mandatory for every student, both tracks.</p>
        <p class="whatfor">Pick Coursera courses adding up to 20 marks. Beginner courses are 5 marks, intermediate are 10. Mix as you like. Then record a short video reflecting on what you learned — that's another 10 marks. This is 30% of your grade and the easiest part to lose because it runs in the background and people forget about it until July.</p>
        <ul class="deadlines">
          <li>Submit all Coursera certificates <small>by 11 Jul</small></li>
          <li>Submit Coursera reflection video <small>by 26 Jul</small></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="marks-line">30 marks · starts tomorrow</div>
      </div>

      <!-- TRACK 1 -->
      <div class="track-card">
        <span class="tag">Track 1 · The mentor route</span>
        <h3>Project with an EPG.</h3>
        <p class="who">For students who can find an External Project Guide.</p>
        <p class="whatfor">Pick a research problem from your industry. Find a senior person willing to mentor you (cannot be a relative). Write a proposal. Do the research. Submit a 25–30 page report. Make a reflection video. The proposal is signed by you, the researcher — not by the EPG.</p>
        <ul class="deadlines">
          <li>EPG details <small>by 17 May</small></li>
          <li>Project Proposal <small>by 31 May</small></li>
          <li>Final Project Report <small>by 11 Jul</small></li>
          <li>Reflection Video <small>by 26 Jul</small></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="marks-line">70 marks · choose by 17 May</div>
      </div>

      <!-- TRACK 2 -->
      <div class="track-card">
        <span class="tag">Track 2 · The fallback</span>
        <h3>Project anchored to a course.</h3>
        <p class="who">For students without an eligible EPG. Auto-assigned if you miss 17 May.</p>
        <p class="whatfor">Pick a problem statement tied to one of the prescribed Coursera courses for Track 2. Complete that specific course. Build the project around it. Submit the same 25–30 page report and reflection video as Track 1. Same total marks.</p>
        <ul class="deadlines">
          <li>Designated Coursera certificate <small>by 31 May</small></li>
          <li>Final Project Report <small>by 11 Jul</small></li>
          <li>Reflection Video <small>by 26 Jul</small></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="marks-line">70 marks · default if 17 May missed</div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TOMORROW -->
  <div class="tomorrow">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div class="section-num">§ 02 — Now do this</div>
      <h2>Tomorrow. <em>This weekend.</em> Next week.</h2>
      <div class="section-sub">Concrete actions for the next ten days. Do these in order. Don't skip ahead.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-grid">

      <div class="day-row">
        <div class="when">
          <div class="label">Step 1</div>
          <div class="when-name">Tomorrow <em>· Friday</em></div>
          <div class="dates">1 May 2026 · 1 task</div>
        </div>
        <div class="what">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="group-label">The only thing that matters tomorrow</div>
            <ul>
              <li>Decide your track. Track 1 (you have or can get an EPG) or Track 2 (you don't). If you're 50/50, default to Track 1 — you can always fall back if your EPG isn't approved.</li>
            </ul>
